1. *Sobom* je doneo slatkiše. (He brought sweets with him.)
2. Oni su se sakrili od *sobom*. (They hid from themselves.)
3. Ona se uvek ponaša po *sobom*. (She always behaves according to herself.)
4. Ona je zauzela stav *sobom*. (She took a stance for herself.)
5. *Sobom* nikada ne kasni. (He never arrives late by himself.)
6. Oni su živeli nezavisno od *sobom*. (They lived independently from themselves.)